OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FLargely dry and bright on Thursday,
OL,7,Fbut rain arriving later. High pressure
OL,8,Fbuilds back in from Friday bringing
OL,9,Fplenty of dry and bright weather, but
OL,10,Ftemperatures returning to nearer
OL,11,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
